OL,5,Cimproved
OL,7,FArena bomb survivor has called on one
OL,8,Fof Manchester's popular venues to do
OL,9,F"better in terms of disabled access
OL,10,Fand viewing areas."
OL,12,FThe football agent from Bolton was the
OL,13,Fclosest person to survive the
OL,14,Fterrorist attack in May 2022 and has
OL,15,Fvisited the Arena a number of times in
OL,16,Fhis wheelchair.
