OL,5,Cimproved
OL,7,FBut he said he won't be taking up his
OL,8,Foffer of replacement tickets to see
OL,9,FTake That at the venue after it was
OL,10,Fcancelled at Manchester's troubled new
OL,11,Fvenue,
OL,13,FHe said the last time he used their
OL,14,Faccessible viewing platform he said
OL,15,Fthey were 'herded in their like
OL,16,Fcattle'.
