OL,5,Cimproved
OL,7,FThe father-of-one said the last time
OL,8,Fhe went into the 'accessible' area at
OL,9,Fthe Arena to watch the two years ago,
OL,10,Fhe was taken to a 'platform' which he
OL,11,Fdescribed as a free-for-all with
OL,12,Flimited space for carers or guests.
OL,14,FHe said only those at the front got a
OL,15,Fdecent view of the stage, with those
OL,16,Fsitting behind left struggling to see.
OL,18,FHe said he'd gone to the show with his
OL,19,Fwife Gabby, who was given a plastic
OL,20,Fchair to sit on next to Martin.
