OL,7,FBut as the platform got busier with
OL,8,Fother wheelchair users, he said she
OL,9,Ffelt she had to move to sit at the
OL,10,Fback on her own to let others 'try to
OL,11,Fhave a better view.'
OL,13,FHe said his experience was even more
OL,14,Fharrowing because he was taken to the
OL,15,Fplatform, using the same lift and
OL,16,Froute, as the bomber Salman Abedi
OL,17,Ftook, to detonate his home-made device
OL,18,Fin the venue's City Room.
