OL,7,FMartin said for him that was 'too
OL,8,Fmuch' going past the place he saw his
OL,9,Fdaughter Evie seriously injured and
OL,10,Fwaiting for help and where he thought
OL,11,Fhe was going to die.
OL,13,FMartin, who is now the Vice President
OL,14,Fof the Spinal Injuries Association
OL,15,F(SIA) is campaigning to make the world
OL,16,Fa better place for disabled people.
OL,18,FHe is urging politicians, planners,
OL,19,Fdevelopers, and businesses to put
OL,20,Fdisabled access higher on their
OL,21,Fagendas, to encourage real change.
