OL,5,Cimproved
OL,7,FHe has been invited to be an advisor
OL,8,Fto the Night-time economy advisor to
OL,9,FGreater Manchester Mayor Andy Burnham
OL,10,Fand says there is so much more the
OL,11,Farea can do to support disabled people.
OL,13,FMartin said for him that was 'too
OL,14,Fmuch' going past the place he saw his
OL,15,Fdaughter Evie seriously injured and
OL,16,Fwaiting for help and where he thought
OL,17,Fhe was going to die.
OL,19,FMartin says he hopes to be able to
OL,20,Ftalk to the Arena team about improving
OL,21,Faccess for other people.
